longBusinessSummary: Intelligent Highway Solutions, Inc. operates as a technology based highway solutions contractor in California. The company focuses on providing labor, materials, and related equipment for corrective and maintenance services for the California state transportation infrastructure. It also installs temperature control systems and associated sensors, as well as engages in the other general electrical contracting works. Intelligent Highway Solutions, Inc. was founded in 2011 and is based in Elk Grove, California.
